Introduction

Nahyun is a South Korean singer signed with AO Entertainment. She is a part of the girl group PRIMROSE. Before this, she used to be the leader of another girl group HOT ISSUE.

Nahyun debuted as a member of HOT ISSUE on April 28, 2021, with the mini-album “Issue Maker”. However, the group disbanded on April 22, 2022, just six days before their first anniversary. According to S2 Entertainment, their former agency, the decision was reached after a lengthy discussion about the group’s future and direction.
